	<span class="f36"><b>Instructions</b></span>
	<br />Gameplay is the same as Reversi <a style="color:skyblue" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Reversi">(See Here)</a>. 
	<br /><span style="color:#b4bdff;">Reversi</span><span style="color:#ffcc00">X</span>, unlike Reversi, is not strictly turn-based and is played on a 16x16 board with 4 players. 
	Moves can be performed at any time and is followed by a 5 second cooldown. 
	To perform a move, simply click on the game board.
